Job Description
One of our prestigious client is looking for a "FIRE Fighter", Firefighting and emergency care, responds to emergency calls to protect life and property • Fights fires, provides medical assistance & performs rescue operations. • Performs fire and hazardous materials inspections of buildings & responds to accidents. Email misc(at)firstselectuae.com
