About This Company
First Select is an international corporate recruitment group with its corporate office in the UAE, which through its network of offices offers a hands on quality service that allows us to source and work with candidates and employers from a wide range of countries.
Right Person’ for the ‘Right Position’, at the ‘Right Price’, at the ‘Right Place’ and at the ‘Right Pace’ ; First Select envisions to be the market innovator in providing Executive Search, Recruitment and Contract Staffing solutions in the Europe, Middle East, North Africa and South Asia.
We provides its services to the regions major Oil, Gas, Petrochemical, Power, Hospitals, Banks, Hotels, Telecom, Construction and Multinational companies
First Select has a team with extensive experience in the Human Resource Management and Recruitment fields in many countries and ensures that the recruitment process is managed to the advantage of the employer as well as the prospective employee.
